{"version":"https://jsonfeed.org/version/1","title":"Micro.blog - manton timeline","home_page_url":"https://micro.blog","feed_url":"https://micro.blog/feeds/manton.json","icon":"https://micro.blog/images/icons/favicon_256.png","favicon":"https://micro.blog/images/icons/favicon_32.png","_microblog":{"about":"https://micro.blog/about/api"},"items":[{"id":"92913646","content_html":"<p class=\"quote-inline\">RE: <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/@jeffjarvis/116812879106726595\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">mastodon.social/@jeffjarvis/11</span><span class=\"invisible\">6812879106726595</span></a></p><p>Sad news.</p><blockquote class=\"quoteback\" data-author=\"jeffjarvis@mastodon.social\" data-avatar=\"https://cdn.micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.social%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F243%2F139%2F631%2F965%2F273%2Foriginal%2Ff9cf9411bc073721.jpg\">\n<p>Oh, no. We've lost a great soul. Om Malik has passed. <a href=\"https://om.co/2026/06/24/1966-2026/\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span>om.co/2026/06/24/1966-2026/</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></p>\n<footer>jeffjarvis@mastodon.social <cite><a href=\"https://mastodon.social/@jeffjarvis/116812879106726595\" class=\"u-in-reply-to\">mastodon.social/@jeffjarvis/116812879106726595</a></cite></footer>\n</blockquote>","url":"https://macaw.social/@andypiper/116813027647194071","date_published":"2026-06-25T22:09:09+00:00","author":{"name":"Andy Piper","url":"https://macaw.social/@andypiper","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Fmacawsocial.sfo3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F332%2F977%2F621%2F728%2F450%2Foriginal%2F950db275ada697f1.jpeg","_microblog":{"username":"andypiper@macaw.social"}}},{"id":"92911626","content_html":"<p>I’m particularly glad today that I didn’t wait for the rumored touch screen/OLED updates to buy my M5 MacBook Pro, although I am nervous about how much the rumored OLED iPad mini I’d planned to buy will be now.</p>","url":"https://mstdn.social/@chipotle/116812926143193745","date_published":"2026-06-25T21:43:19+00:00","author":{"name":"Watts Martin","url":"https://mstdn.social/@chipotle","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.mstdn.social%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F510%2F207%2F631%2F147%2F430%2Foriginal%2F794c26587dc6a591.jpeg","_microblog":{"username":"chipotle@mstdn.social"}}},{"id":"92911561","content_html":"<p>Well how about that, we've (almost) booted to desktop</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.micro.blog/photos/1000x/https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.social%2Fmedia_attachments%2Ffiles%2F116%2F812%2F917%2F613%2F303%2F716%2Foriginal%2Fd94a1b552a90ef84.jpeg\" alt=\"Macintosh menu bar and checkerboard desktop pattern, some windows onscreen (with pixel corruption), in qemu-system-arm\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>","url":"https://mastodon.social/users/stroughtonsmith/statuses/116812917868573055","date_published":"2026-06-25T21:41:13+00:00","author":{"name":"Steve Troughton-Smith","url":"https://mastodon.social/@stroughtonsmith","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.social%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F742%2F206%2F677%2F653%2F822%2Foriginal%2Fcf30d22950290178.jpeg","_microblog":{"username":"stroughtonsmith@mastodon.social"}}},{"id":"92910463","content_html":"<p>I found this piece from an anthology celebrating 50 years of women’s studies, which explores <a href=\"https://uw.pressbooks.pub/happy50thws/chapter/from-theory-to-content-feminist-publishing-makes-womens-studies-powerful/\">the intersection of scholarship and publishing practices over time</a>.</p>\n","url":"https://flotisserie.micro.blog/2026/06/25/i-found-this-piece-from.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T21:27:25+00:00","author":{"name":"Lauren","url":"https://flotisserie.micro.blog/","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2026/13/1504092.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"flotisserie"}}},{"id":"92910305","content_html":"<p>Submitting my next-to-last timesheet, which is just burning through vacation time. The last one will be the last two days of June. It is very weird to have my job end while I am on vacation, but life is often very weird.</p>","url":"https://mstdn.social/@chipotle/116812852798561492","date_published":"2026-06-25T21:24:40+00:00","author":{"name":"Watts Martin","url":"https://mstdn.social/@chipotle","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.mstdn.social%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F510%2F207%2F631%2F147%2F430%2Foriginal%2F794c26587dc6a591.jpeg","_microblog":{"username":"chipotle@mstdn.social"}}},{"id":"92910306","content_html":"<p>never met Om, but a sane voice that I will very much miss</p><p>read his recent essays when you get a chance</p><p><a href=\"https://om.co/2026/06/24/1966-2026/\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span>om.co/2026/06/24/1966-2026/</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></p>","url":"https://podcastindex.social/@js/116812852722077967","date_published":"2026-06-25T21:24:39+00:00","author":{"name":"John Spurlock","url":"https://podcastindex.social/@js","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.masto.host%2Fpodcastindexsocial%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F000%2F002%2F616%2Foriginal%2F291302db1e78b81e.jpeg","_microblog":{"username":"js@podcastindex.social"}}},{"id":"92909514","content_html":"<p>Heartbreaking to hear that <a href=\"https://om.co/2026/06/24/1966-2026/\">Om Malik has passed away</a>. I can hardly believe it. Even just this year, it felt like he was doing some of his best writing. Very thankful for the time he gave us at Micro Camp 2023… I was so excited to talk to him. Rest in peace.</p>\n","url":"https://www.manton.org/2026/06/25/heartbreaking-to-hear-that-om.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T21:16:14+00:00","author":{"name":"Manton Reece","url":"https://manton.org","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2025/22/3.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"manton"}}},{"id":"92909513","content_html":"<p>My new Kobo ebook reader got delivered today from Kobo.com.  Easiest setup ever.  More update to follow after I use it.  I wanted to charge it up after I got it running and sync’d.</p>\n","url":"https://ramblinggit.com/2026/06/25/my-new-kobo-ebook-reader.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T21:15:58+00:00","author":{"name":"Brad Enslen ","url":"https://ramblinggit.com/","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2025/08/8742.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"bradenslen"}}},{"id":"92908715","content_html":"<p>I don’t want to sound too <em>alarmist</em> to my German friends but Ecuador are pressing like motherfuckers!</p>\n","url":"https://www.tibz.blog/2026/06/25/i-dont-want-to-sound.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T21:00:01+00:00","author":{"name":"Thibault Lemaitre","url":"http://tibz.blog","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2022/706.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"tibz"}}},{"id":"92908666","content_html":"<p>AAPL ended the day even worse than that</p><p>worst single day in over a year</p><p><a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/06/25/apple-macbook-ipad-price-hike-memory.html\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">cnbc.com/2026/06/25/apple-macb</span><span class=\"invisible\">ook-ipad-price-hike-memory.html</span></a></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.micro.blog/photos/1000x/https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.masto.host%2Fpodcastindexsocial%2Fmedia_attachments%2Ffiles%2F116%2F812%2F750%2F610%2F992%2F267%2Foriginal%2F3cf646c421bf1083.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>","url":"https://podcastindex.social/users/js/statuses/116812751315113651","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:58:52+00:00","author":{"name":"John Spurlock","url":"https://podcastindex.social/@js","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.masto.host%2Fpodcastindexsocial%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F000%2F002%2F616%2Foriginal%2F291302db1e78b81e.jpeg","_microblog":{"username":"js@podcastindex.social"}}},{"id":"92908689","content_html":"<div class=\"media-gallery\">\n                                                    <img class=\"media-item\" src=\"https://cdn.uploads.micro.blog/209740/2026/h3rwa7ad3qkxpuysf306zxfhioid2n12rruw43rj-m.jpg\" alt=\"dragonfly on a grass stalk\" loading=\"lazy\">\n                                            </div>\n                    <p>This skimmer was just hanging out (literally) in the tall grass when I walked by this morning.<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pxlmo.com/discover/tags/dailyphoto?src=hash\" title=\"#dailyphoto\" class=\"u-url hashtag\">#dailyphoto</a> <a href=\"https://pxlmo.com/discover/tags/oregon?src=hash\" title=\"#oregon\" class=\"u-url hashtag\">#oregon</a> <a href=\"https://pxlmo.com/discover/tags/eugeneoregon?src=hash\" title=\"#eugeneoregon\" class=\"u-url hashtag\">#eugeneoregon</a> <a href=\"https://pxlmo.com/discover/tags/insectphotography?src=hash\" title=\"#insectphotography\" class=\"u-url hashtag\">#insectphotography</a></p>\n","url":"https://larkfarm.com/2026/06/25/this-skimmer-was-just-hanging.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:58:21+00:00","author":{"name":"Mike Gunderloy","url":"https://ffmike.micro.blog/","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2025/09/1736181.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"ffmike"}}},{"id":"92908546","content_html":"<p>paging <a href=\"https://micro.blog/dave\">@dave</a> who I’m sure will have an opinion ..</p>\n<p>// <a href=\"https://micro.blog/johnbrayton\">@johnbrayton</a> <a href=\"https://micro.blog/manton\">@manton</a> <a href=\"https://micro.blog/brentsimmons\">@brentsimmons</a> <a href=\"https://micro.blog/fahrni\">@fahrni</a></p>\n<p>(#BeyondMyPaygrade … but observing how many cool readers have appeared this year .. that all seem to have a slightly different take)</p>\n","url":"https://micro.blog/JohnPhilpin/92908546","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:55:33+00:00","author":{"name":"John PHI⑊PIN","url":"https://john.philpin.com","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2025/50/4165.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"JohnPhilpin"}}},{"id":"92908445","content_html":"<p>I’m shocked and saddened to hear about the <a href=\"https://om.co/2026/06/24/1966-2026/\">passing of Om Malik</a>. I only recently started following his work, but I really liked his attitude to what he was doing, and his optimism towards the future. I regret not following him sooner. My condolence to his friends and family.</p>\n","url":"https://lmika.org/2026/06/26/im-shocked-and-saddened-to.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:53:22+00:00","author":{"name":"Leon Mika","url":"https://lmika.org/","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2024/15/55331.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"lmika"}}},{"id":"92908407","content_html":"<p>Thursday links: <a href=\"https://blog.miljko.org/2026/06/25/thursday-links.html\">blog.miljko.org</a></p>","url":"https://blog.miljko.org/2026/06/25/thursday-links.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:51:35+00:00","author":{"name":"Miloš Miljković","url":"https://miljko.org/","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2022/106160.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"miljko"}}},{"id":"92908182","content_html":"<p>Om Malik was a rock in the Mac community. <a href=\"https://om.co/2026/06/24/1966-2026/\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span>om.co/2026/06/24/1966-2026/</span><span class=\"invisible\"></span></a></p>","url":"https://mastodon.social/@Cdespinosa/116812701602359822","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:46:13+00:00","author":{"name":"Chris Espinosa","url":"https://mastodon.social/@Cdespinosa","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.social%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F000%2F228%2F566%2Foriginal%2F4fb389ce6e420e36.png","_microblog":{"username":"Cdespinosa@mastodon.social"}}},{"id":"92907464","content_html":"<p>Hitze: <a href=\"https://janlukas.blog/de/gedanken/2026/06/hitze\">janlukas.blog</a></p>","url":"https://janlukas.blog/de/gedanken/2026/06/hitze","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:38:23+00:00","author":{"name":"Jan-Lukas Else","url":"https://janlukas.blog","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2022/38437.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"jlelse"}},"summary":"Jeder schreibt über Klimaanlagen und die Hitze, also will ich auch mal kurz meine Gedanken dazu teilen. Wer weiß, ob man schon in wenigen Jahren über die 40 Grad und den Aufruhr deswegen nur noch müde lächeln kann."},{"id":"92907315","content_html":"<p>Stunned and saddened to read that <a href=\"https://om.co/2026/06/24/1966-2026/\">Om Malik has passed</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Om Malik passed away on June 24, 2026, at Stanford Hospital after a long health journey with his heart. He was surrounded by family and friends.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>My condolences to his loved ones. I’ve been reading Om’s blog for years and always enjoyed his insight, and especially his interweaved creative endeavors. <a href=\"https://www.photosbyom.com/\">His photography</a> has always been striking. He’ll be missed.</p>\n<p>Om’s <a href=\"https://om.co/2026/06/08/taking-a-few-days-off/\">most recent post</a> was a personal note saying he was taking a break for some time to himself, and to read some mystery novels. I hope he enjoyed them. His final sign off:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Be well.</p>\n</blockquote>\n","url":"https://jb.heydingus.net/2026/06/25/stunned-and-saddened-to-read.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:36:46+00:00","author":{"name":"Jarrod Blundy","url":"http://jb.heydingus.net","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2023/02/5676.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"jarrod"}}},{"id":"92906929","content_html":"<p><a href=\"https://babylonbee.com/news/weakling-french-declare-hottest-day-ever-when-its-only-40-degrees/\">Weakling French Declare ‘Hottest Day Ever’ When It’s Only 40 Degrees - Babylon Bee</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Facing weather that most Americans would take on with a hoodie, the pitiful French warned that hundreds of people across the country could perish.</p>\n</blockquote>\n","url":"https://chetjcollins.com/2026/06/25/weakling-french-declare-hottest-day.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:31:50+00:00","author":{"name":"Chet Collins","url":"","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2026/18/2987.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"chet"}}},{"id":"92906384","content_html":"<p>It’s beautiful outside today. The current temperature is 86F(30C) but it doesn’t feel that hot in the shade with a slight breeze.</p>\n<p>I’m on our back deck enjoying a beer and our beautiful blue sky.</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.uploads.micro.blog/5176/2026/e6ead7ff12-m.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" alt=\"Picture of trees with a blue sky and a few white clouds.\" loading=\"lazy\">\n","url":"https://rob.crabapples.net/2026/06/25/its-beautiful-outside-today-the.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:26:51+00:00","author":{"name":"Rob Fahrni","url":"https://fahrni.me","avatar":"https://micro.blog/fahrni/avatar.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"fahrni"}}},{"id":"92906381","content_html":"<p>It's sad that Bungie is having layoffs. Sony management clearly over-focused on service-based games across all of their first party teams.</p><p>I hope that the reductions aren't going to affect their ability to start building single player games in addition to keeping their Marathon service-based game healthy.</p>","url":"https://mastodon.online/@alexr/116812625056281721","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:26:45+00:00","author":{"name":"Alex Rosenberg","url":"https://mastodon.online/@alexr","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.online%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F108%2F195%2F349%2F335%2F944%2F180%2Foriginal%2F81034ba16b54d492.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"alexr@mastodon.online"}}},{"id":"92905815","content_html":"<p>From the samples I've taken, about 0.85% of accounts on the Fediverse are Group actors. <a href=\"https://cosocial.ca/tags/activitypub\" class=\"mention hashtag\">#<span>activitypub</span></a> <a href=\"https://cosocial.ca/tags/groups\" class=\"mention hashtag\">#<span>groups</span></a></p>","url":"https://cosocial.ca/@evan/116812604126322238","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:21:26+00:00","author":{"name":"Evan Prodromou","url":"https://cosocial.ca/@evan","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Fm.f-h.co%2Fcosocial-ca%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F493%2F705%2F899%2F503%2F027%2Foriginal%2F161d79af33d78831.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"evan@cosocial.ca"}}},{"id":"92905094","content_html":"<p>(And if nobody knows how any of this stuff works, developers aren't going to bother trying to build for it until somebody documents it)</p>","url":"https://mastodon.social/users/stroughtonsmith/statuses/116812573534185434","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:13:39+00:00","author":{"name":"Steve Troughton-Smith","url":"https://mastodon.social/@stroughtonsmith","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.social%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F742%2F206%2F677%2F653%2F822%2Foriginal%2Fcf30d22950290178.jpeg","_microblog":{"username":"stroughtonsmith@mastodon.social"}}},{"id":"92905023","content_html":"<p>There is a pile of new AppIntent-based APIs to make your apps' content available to Siri AI, but it doesn't seem like there's any way at all to actually debug what Siri is seeing or doing with it. And since you never know whether you have an app intent failure, or Siri's LLM has decided just not to use it when queried, this stuff feels like a mess to figure out. I wish there were some kind of debug commandline interface to Siri that scopes purely to the actions available to your app ID</p>","url":"https://mastodon.social/@stroughtonsmith/116812569599066066","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:12:39+00:00","author":{"name":"Steve Troughton-Smith","url":"https://mastodon.social/@stroughtonsmith","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.social%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F742%2F206%2F677%2F653%2F822%2Foriginal%2Fcf30d22950290178.jpeg","_microblog":{"username":"stroughtonsmith@mastodon.social"}}},{"id":"92903810","content_html":"<div class=\"e-content\">\n<p>Some time ago <a href=\"https://janlukas.blog/micro/2026/03/2026-03-08-rhpzv\">I posted about my experience</a> blocking one country and some ASNs directly via iptables from my mail server. It seems like there’s an even better source of IPs and networks to block.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.spamhaus.org/blocklists/do-not-route-or-peer/\">The Spamhaus “Don’t Route Or Peer Lists (DROP)” lists.</a></p>\n<p>Currently my mail setup is configured to block everything...</p>\n</div> <a href=\"https://janlukas.blog/micro/2026/06/2026-06-25-sevyd\">janlukas.blog</a>","url":"https://janlukas.blog/micro/2026/06/2026-06-25-sevyd","date_published":"2026-06-25T20:02:11+00:00","author":{"name":"Jan-Lukas Else","url":"https://janlukas.blog","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2022/38437.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"jlelse"}}},{"id":"92903416","content_html":"<img src=\"https://cdn.uploads.micro.blog/404/2026/img-0341-m.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n","url":"https://social.ayjay.org/2026/06/25/145712.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T19:57:12+00:00","author":{"name":"Alan Jacobs ","url":"https://ayjay.org","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2022/650.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"ayjay"}}},{"id":"92903012","content_html":"<p>Got me some back shots today for my stenosis and the numbing shot hasn't worn off yet, so at this point I think it was a great idea.</p>","url":"https://hachyderm.io/@ttscoff/116812506924185990","date_published":"2026-06-25T19:56:43+00:00","author":{"name":"Brett Terpstra 🏴🐈‍⬛","url":"https://hachyderm.io/@ttscoff","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.mas.to%2Fcache%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F113%2F923%2F275%2F022%2F233%2F901%2Foriginal%2F82c8576531b0b09e.jpeg","_microblog":{"username":"ttscoff@hachyderm.io"}}},{"id":"92902948","content_html":"<p>Nice day for ballgame!</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.micro.blog/photos/1000x/https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.social%2Fmedia_attachments%2Ffiles%2F116%2F812%2F503%2F397%2F256%2F818%2Foriginal%2F2f5d934dda2e7190.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>","url":"https://mastodon.social/@kocienda/116812503669490211","date_published":"2026-06-25T19:55:53+00:00","author":{"name":"Ken Kocienda","url":"https://mastodon.social/@kocienda","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.social%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F544%2F332%2F896%2F078%2F440%2Foriginal%2Fac6db34f3b053dd1.png","_microblog":{"username":"kocienda@mastodon.social"}}},{"id":"92902517","content_html":"<p>Ontem cruzei com crianças fazendo e vendendo essas pulseiras e comprei pra ajudar. Disse que meu nome era “Campos” porque é mais fácil de escrever.</p><p>Na hora nem me ocorreu, mas agora estou aqui pensando que deveria ter pedido para escreverem “vladcampos” 😊</p><p><img src=\"https://cdn.micro.blog/photos/1000x/https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.social%2Fmedia_attachments%2Ffiles%2F116%2F812%2F486%2F863%2F039%2F023%2Foriginal%2F3d98eb161d62d774.jpg\" alt=\"2026-06-25 19.37 Pulseira Campos.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>","url":"https://mastodon.social/@vladcampos/116812486918222376","date_published":"2026-06-25T19:51:37+00:00","author":{"name":"Vladimir Campos","url":"https://mastodon.social/@vladcampos","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Ffiles.mastodon.social%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F108%2F180%2F111%2F114%2F951%2F917%2Foriginal%2F0bf524b8092368b2.png","_microblog":{"username":"vladcampos@mastodon.social"}}},{"id":"92903197","content_html":"<p>I was Too Angry and now instagram is exclusively showing me stuff that makes me mad.</p><p><a href=\"https://bsky.app/profile/did:plc:xkn7cc6syz3pz56mzfn4zpp7/post/3mp52wa27ec2v\">I'm not going to come on here and be angry again I've already been angry today.</a></p>","url":"https://bsky.app/profile/did:plc:xkn7cc6syz3pz56mzfn4zpp7/post/3mp56xnzqw22j","date_published":"2026-06-25T19:45:16+00:00","author":{"name":"Abby Roberts","url":"http://arobertswrites.com/","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Farobertswrites.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsphinx-edited.png%3Fw%3D200","_microblog":{"username":"arobertswrites.com"}}},{"id":"92901841","content_html":"<p>This is most emails. <a href=\"https://mastodon.social/@thisemailfindsyou/116812421655811037\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">mastodon.social/@thisemailfind</span><span class=\"invisible\">syou/116812421655811037</span></a></p>","url":"https://c.im/@nickheer/116812459884361419","date_published":"2026-06-25T19:44:45+00:00","author":{"name":"Nick Heer","url":"https://c.im/@nickheer","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Fs3.c.im%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F322%2F424%2F767%2F638%2F126%2Foriginal%2F937bc5d2c4bb11c2.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"nickheer@c.im"}}},{"id":"92901265","content_html":"<p>Bubbles: <a href=\"https://eay.cc/2026/bubbles/\">eay.cc</a></p>","url":"https://eay.cc/2026/bubbles/","date_published":"2026-06-25T19:37:29+00:00","author":{"name":"Stefan Grund","url":"https://eay.cc","avatar":"https://micro.blog/eay/avatar.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"eay"}}},{"id":"92900142","content_html":"<p>Etter sju måneder klarte jeg endelig å manne meg opp til å se ferdig første episode av Pluribus. Tror resten skal gå litt enklere.</p>\n","url":"https://teisam.net/2026/06/25/etter-sju-mneder-klarte-jeg.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T19:20:10+00:00","author":{"name":"Tor Einar Samdahl","url":"","avatar":"https://micro.blog/teisam/avatar.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"teisam"}}},{"id":"92899889","content_html":"<img src=\"https://cdn.uploads.micro.blog/122424/2026/726188e8e3-m.jpg\" width=\"450\" height=\"600\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\">\n","url":"https://robertbrook.micro.blog/2026/06/25/201521.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T19:15:21+00:00","author":{"name":"Robert Brook","url":"https://robert-brook.com/","avatar":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/04317a68133d7c213b66def2e0ee8145?s=96&d=https%3A%2F%2Fmicro.blog%2Fimages%2Fblank_avatar.png","_microblog":{"username":"robertbrook"}}},{"id":"92900962","content_html":"<p>Asides: Jun 25: <a href=\"https://www.amitgawande.com/blog/2026/notes-2026-06-25/\">amitgawande.com</a></p>","url":"https://www.amitgawande.com/blog/2026/notes-2026-06-25/","date_published":"2026-06-25T19:15:03+00:00","author":{"name":"Amit Gawande","url":"https://amitg.blog/","avatar":"https://avatars.micro.blog/avatars/2023/35/2885.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"amit"}},"summary":"06:49 I have started cursing a lot in my journal. Wither state of my mind or am becoming free. Two extreme ends.\n\n22:55 I don’t like wireless mouse with rechargeable battery. It starts running out faster and then becomes just wired ones.\n\nReply to this post"},{"id":"92898509","content_html":"<p>UIKit engineers: here's your chance to explain what the hell is going on with horizontalSizeClass and to hopefully improve the developer experience behind the change.</p><p><a href=\"https://developer.apple.com/forums/thread/836088\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">developer.apple.com/forums/thr</span><span class=\"invisible\">ead/836088</span></a></p>","url":"https://mastodon.social/users/chockenberry/statuses/116812285598042128","date_published":"2026-06-25T19:00:25+00:00","author":{"name":"Craig Hockenberry","url":"https://mastodon.social/@chockenberry","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.mas.to%2Fcache%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F263%2F290%2F746%2F572%2F231%2Foriginal%2F0c5fdbd335ec351b.jpeg","_microblog":{"username":"chockenberry@mastodon.social"}}},{"id":"92898440","content_html":"<p>Tomorrow InshaAllah, I am looking forward to breakfast with Helena and Maurice</p>\n","url":"https://diplomaticdiva.micro.blog/2026/06/25/tomorrow-inshaallah-i-am-looking.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T18:59:08+00:00","author":{"name":"Diplomatic Diva","url":"http://dailyd1va.wordpress.com","avatar":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/cc90b5b8480866e8f3c57118c2150090?s=96&d=https%3A%2F%2Fmicro.blog%2Fimages%2Fblank_avatar.png","_microblog":{"username":"DiplomaticDiva"}}},{"id":"92898421","content_html":"<p>I wonder how this drama would have played out on Fedi.  Obviously Ken would have been reported and I suspect that on our instance, our moderation team would have insisted he rephrase his post or have it taken down.   I wonder if that would be typical…</p><p><a href=\"https://www.popehat.com/p/a-bit-of-tedious-drama-at-bluesky\"><span class=\"invisible\">https://www.</span><span class=\"ellipsis\">popehat.com/p/a-bit-of-tedious</span><span class=\"invisible\">-drama-at-bluesky</span></a></p>","url":"https://cosocial.ca/@timbray/116812278432355638","date_published":"2026-06-25T18:58:36+00:00","author":{"name":"Tim Bray 🇨🇦","url":"https://cosocial.ca/@timbray","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Fm.f-h.co%2Fcosocial-ca%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F109%2F493%2F862%2F422%2F378%2F324%2Foriginal%2F9b63cd825f07f89d.jpg","_microblog":{"username":"timbray@cosocial.ca"}}},{"id":"92898409","content_html":"<p>Today I was grateful for strawberries</p>\n","url":"https://diplomaticdiva.micro.blog/2026/06/25/today-i-was-grateful-for.html","date_published":"2026-06-25T18:58:21+00:00","author":{"name":"Diplomatic Diva","url":"http://dailyd1va.wordpress.com","avatar":"https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/cc90b5b8480866e8f3c57118c2150090?s=96&d=https%3A%2F%2Fmicro.blog%2Fimages%2Fblank_avatar.png","_microblog":{"username":"DiplomaticDiva"}}},{"id":"92898081","content_html":"<p>Woe-driven development.</p>","url":"https://mastodon.social/users/bigzaphod/statuses/116812266742325533","date_published":"2026-06-25T18:55:38+00:00","author":{"name":"Sean Heber","url":"https://mastodon.social/@bigzaphod","avatar":"https://micro.blog/photos/200/https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.mas.to%2Fcache%2Faccounts%2Favatars%2F000%2F057%2F451%2Foriginal%2F8f5320374ea87b09.png","_microblog":{"username":"bigzaphod@mastodon.social"}}},{"id":"92903198","content_html":"<p>I have adhd so I don't have either.</p